    <title>Zym_Array</title>
    <para>
        <code>Zym_Array</code> provides two interfaces to set data from an array 
        and to get data as an array. These are useful to ensure that a certain
        api will be available.
    </para>
    
    <section xml:id="zym.array.from.interface">
        <title>From array interface</title>
        
        <para>
            <code>Zym_Array_From_Interface</code> provides the <code>setFromArray()</code> method.
        </para>
        
